Package Scrapper.Items

package Scrapper.Items
Houses all the types of items that will be read and written into the final file. Should include all item types encountered, eg. Unspoiled Nodes (here: https://ffxiv.consolegameswiki.com/wiki/Unspoiled_Nodes) has a class of its own. The arguments should be all the table headers.
